tasks.description:
In server/routes.ts /api/gemini/chat, when stream=true: use Gemini's generateContentStream() instead of sendMessage(). Set response headers to text/event-stream. Write SSE chunks as 'data: {"text": "..."}

' for each token. End with 'data: [DONE]

'. Keep the non-streaming path as fallback when stream=false. The client-side SSE parser already exists in BabylonChatPanel.ts lines 1117-1150 — match that expected format.
